Title: An Act Changing the Name of Sto. Niño Elementary School in the Municipality of Jose Abad Santos, Province of Davao Del Sur, to Badal Yuba Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 752
An Act Changing the Name of Sto. Niño Elementary School in the Municipality of Jose Abad Santos, Province of Davao Del Sur, to Badal Yuba Elementary School
Section 1. The name of Sto. Niño Elementary School in the Municipality of Jose Abad Santos, Province of Davao del Sur, is changed to Badal Yuba Elementary School.1awphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
